powered.description: Whether the command block is powered by redstone

conditionMet.description:
Whether the previous command block was successful when the command block was executed  
 This is always true for non-conditional command blocks

UpdateLastExecution.description: Whether to update the tick that this command block last executed

TrackOutput.description: Whether the command block should track its output

Command.description: The command stored in the command block

SuccessCount.description: The success count of the last command

auto.description: Whether the command block is automatically powered

LastOutput.description: The last output of the command block

LastExecution.description: The tick the command block last executed in

ExactTeleport.description: Whether the portal should teleport to the exact location

Age.description: The age of the portal in ticks

ExitPortal.description: The coordinates of where to teleport entities to

X.description: The x coordinate of the teleport location

Y.description: The y coordinate of the teleport location

Z.description: The z coordinate of the teleport location

TransferCooldown.description: The number of ticks until an item can be transfered

LootTable.description: The loot table that will populate this container

Lock.description: The name of the item that a player has to be holding to open this container

Items.description: The items in this container, with slots from 0 to 4

LootTableSeed.description: The seed of the loot table

Text4.description: The fourth line of text from the top

Text2.description: The second line of text from the top

Text3.description: The third line of text from the top

Color.description: The color the sign has been dyed

Text1.description: The first line of text from the top

Target.description: The UUID of the conduit's target

Items.description: The items that are currently cooking

CookingTotalTimes.description:
The time each item has to cook  
 Index zero is slot zero, etc

CookingTimes.description:
The time each item has been cooking  
 Index zero is slot zero, etc

RightOfDiagonal.description: Right of Diagonal (Per bend sinister inverted)

LeftOfUpsideDownDiagonal.description: Left of upside-down Diagonal (Per bend inverted)

Multiplicative.description:
Multiplies the current value of the attribute by (1 + x),
 where x is the sum of the modifiers' amounts.

Additive.description: Adds all of the modifiers' amounts to the current value of the attribute

Percentage.description:
For every modifier, multiplies the current value of the attribute by (1 + x),
 where x is the amount of the particular modifier.
 Functions the same as Operation 1 if there is only a single modifier with operation 1 or 2.
 However, for multiple modifiers it will multiply the modifiers rather than adding them
